    📜 **Objective:** (What you two will build/discuss)
    💎 **Loot:** (Potential outcome/learnings)
    Keep it concise, energetic, and under 100 words. Respond in English or Traditional Chinese depending on the user's input language.`;

    try {
      const url = `https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models/gemini-2.5-flash-preview-09-2025:generateContent?key=${apiKey}`;
      const payload = {
        contents: [{ parts: [{ text: prompt }] }],
      };

      const result = await fetchWithBackoff(url, {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
        body: JSON.stringify(payload)
      });

      const text = result.candidates?.[0]?.content?.parts?.[0]?.text;
      if (text) {
        setGeneratedQuest(text);
      } else {
        setApiError("Quest generation failed. The Oracle is currently unresponsive.");
